{"ts":"2026-06-27T06:06:57.690Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Addressing Build Timeouts**\n\nI've just observed an npm build timeout; it's a common issue with Next.js production builds. The default 30-second limit isn't sufficient for complex projects. My current plan is to explore solutions. I'll test with `npx tsc --noEmit` and shorter build steps to optimize or just allow clean edits.\n\n\n**Refining UI Design**\n\nOkay, I've shifted focus to `app/admin/users/page.tsx`. Now, I'm designing a detailed, interactive interface according to the UI Constitution. I'm focusing on user roles and actions. I need to make sure the interface includes a local state for users, filter controls, and beautiful UI elements, including a header. I'm taking this step-by-step to be certain this is fully-featured.\n\n\n**Defining User Roles & Permissions**\n\nI'm now diving deep into user roles and permissions for the System Operator Registry. I'm building out a detailed list, starting with `gff_admin` permissions, and will map those to each user. The plan is to have real-time updates as user roles change. I'm focusing on scope definitions like `global:admin`, `write:governance`, `manage:users`, and `manage:clients`, which will directly impact the interface.\n\n\n**Mapping Permission Granularity**\n\nI'm now detailing `client_admin` and `client_member` permissions, creating a matrix of granted and denied scopes. I'm focusing on defining restrictions for the `client_admin` role, especially regarding `global:admin`, `write:governance`, and specific admin scopes. I'm also ensuring that telemetry and project access are tenant-restricted. I want a clear delineation.\n\n\n**Visualizing Permissions Matrix**\n\nI'm now designing the user interface for the permissions board, focusing on a clear, professional visual representation. I'm thinking a grid layout with green \"GRANTED\" indicators (check icon) and red \"DENIED\" indicators (shield-lock/x-mark icon) for each permission. This is for all client and user scopes.\nI've also reviewed the mock data in `lib/mock-data-model.ts`, specifically client accounts.\nMy goal is a clean, easy-to-understand display that won't require manual interpretation. I'm focusing on simplicity and clarity. I'll make sure to use safe imports, so it does not fail.\n\n\n**Enumerating Icon Library**\n\nI've enumerated a comprehensive icon library including `Search`, `Plus`, `User`, and other relevant symbols. I'm prioritizing the use of locally-built components to minimize external dependencies and ensure a consistent aesthetic. My focus is on enriching the interface without relying on external assets. I'm focusing on UI consistency. I'll make sure there's enough detail to keep a great user experience.\n\n\\n\\n\n\nI've started building the invite user modal. It will include fields for Full Name, Secure Email, and Tenant selection. The tenant dropdown will populate from `previewClientAccounts` and include \"GFF Central Enclave\". I'll also add a role selection with options for `gff_admin`, `client_admin`, and `client_member`. Upon submission, a new user will be created and added to the `users` state, with the selected user immediately displayed. A secure operator ID like `usr-007` will also be generated.\n\n\n**Implementing User Notifications**\n\nI'm now implementing the UI for role changes and operator deactivation. For role changes, a dropdown or radio selector will update a user's role in local state, followed by a \"SSO Directory sync\" success toast with the username and new role. For deactivation, an \"Deactivate Access\" button toggles a user to \"inactive\" with a \"SECURITY ALERT\" notification about revoked session keys, while \"Activate Access\" restores access with an \"SSO Directory\" success toast. I'll make sure these are implemented securely.\n\n\n**Designing Key Roll-over**\n\nI'm now implementing the UI elements for key roll-over events. I'll include a clear backend/auth notice and a premium design with a subtle animated background grid, a narrative timeline or interactive permission map, and a bento grid layout. The page will be fully responsive, with mobile and desktop layouts. It will have clean TSX syntax and match the landing page theme.\n\n\n**Matching Color Scheme**\n\n\\n\\n\n\nI'm now zeroing in on UI color consistency. I've re-examined `app/admin/layout.tsx` and the `PrivateAppShell` component, identifying the dominant dark theme and key color styles like `#020202`, and glowing greens and blues. My goal is for new elements to align with the existing look. I've defined a set of custom cards to ensure uniform styling across the admin interface, and the use of colors like text `#00FFC2` and `#009DFF` for glowing effects. I want my design to be intuitive.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T06:06:57.728Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"5397f3bk","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/admin/users/page.tsx","old_text":null,"new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState, useEffect } from \"react\";\nimport { \n  previewClientAccounts, \n  ClientAccount \n} from \"@/lib/mock-data-model\";\nimport { \n  Search, Plus, User, Shield, Check, Copy, X, ChevronRight, \n  Info, Clock, AlertTriangle, CheckCircle2, Building, RefreshCw, \n  Lock, Unlock, ShieldAlert, BadgeCheck, UserCheck, UserX, Key, \n  Mail, Fingerprint, AlertCircle, HelpCircle, Server\n} from \"lucide-react\";\n\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n// 1. DATA MODELS & TYPES\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\ninterface Operator {\n  id: string;\n  name: string;\n  email: string;\n  role: \"gff_admin\" | \"client_admin\" | \"client_member\";\n  client: string;\n  status: \"active\" | \"inactive\" | \"pending\";\n  clearance: string;\n  fido2State: \"SECURED (FIDO2)\" | \"NOT REGISTERED\" | \"TOKEN DEACTIVATED\" | \"ROLLED-OVER\";\n  lastActive: string;\n}\n\n// Map roles to human-friendly metadata\nconst ROLE_DETAILS = {\n  gff_admin: {\n    label: \"Global Admin (gff_admin)\",\n    badgeColor: \"bg-red-500/10 text-red-400 border-red-500/20\",\n    description: \"Root-level supervisor with cross-tenant cryptographic capabilities and system configuration access.\",\n    clearance: \"CLEARANCE LEVEL V (SECURE SUPERUSER)\",\n    scopes: [\n      { id: \"global:admin\", label: \"Global Root Access\", description: \"Direct root execution inside all sandboxes\", allowed: true },\n      { id: \"write:governance\", label: \"Mutate Guardrails\", description: \"Configure global ISO-27001 policy checks\", allowed: true },\n      { id: \"manage:users\", label: \"User Administration\", description: \"Invite, deactivate, and roll keys for all users\", allowed: true },\n      { id: \"manage:clients\", label: \"Tenant Provisioning\", description: \"Spin up and teardown client sandboxes\", allowed: true },\n      { id: \"read:telemetry\", label: \"Global Telemetry\", description: \"Real-time access to global CPU/Memory streams\", allowed: true },\n      { id: \"write:telemetry\", label: \"Modify Telemetry\", description: \"Adjust enclave allocation parameters\", allowed: true },\n      { id: \"read:projects\", label: \"Global Projects View\", description: \"Inspect active multi-agent sandbox layers\", allowed: true },\n      { id: \"write:projects\", label: \"Create Sandbox Layers\", description: \"Deploy new isolated project spaces\", allowed: true }\n    ]\n  },\n  client_admin: {\n    label: \"Tenant Admin (client_admin)\",\n    badgeColor: \"bg-[#009DFF]/10 text-[#009DFF] border-[#009DFF]/20\",\n    description: \"Administrator restricted to a single client tenant's sandboxes, telemetry, and project teams.\",\n    clearance: \"CLEARANCE LEVEL III (SANDBOX OPERATOR)\",\n    scopes: [\n      { id: \"global:admin\", label: \"Global Root Access\", description: \"Direct root execution inside all sandboxes\", allowed: false },\n      { id: \"write:governance\", label: \"Mutate Guardrails\", description: \"Configure global ISO-27001 policy checks\", allowed: false },\n      { id: \"manage:users\", label: \"User Administration\", description: \"Manage operator keys inside own tenant boundaries\", allowed: true },\n      { id: \"manage:clients\", label: \"Tenant Provisioning\", description: \"Spin up and teardown client sandboxes\", allowed: false },\n      { id: \"read:telemetry\", label: \"Global Telemetry\", description: \"Real-time access to tenant-bound telemetry\", allowed: true },\n      { id: \"write:telemetry\", label: \"Modify Telemetry\", description: \"Adjust local enclave parameters\", allowed: true },\n      { id: \"read:projects\", label: \"Global Projects View\", description: \"Inspect local tenant sandbox layers\", allowed: true },\n      { id: \"write:projects\", label: \"Create Sandbox Layers\", description: \"Deploy new isolated project spaces\", allowed: true }\n    ]\n  },\n  client_member: {\n    label: \"Tenant Member (client_member)\",\n    badgeColor: \"bg-zinc-500/10 text-zinc-400 border-zinc-500/20\",\n    description: \"Standard tenant operator with read-only dashboard insights and basic sandbox execution capabilities.\",\n    clearance: \"CLEARANCE LEVEL II (TENANT OPERATOR)\",\n    scopes: [\n      { id: \"global:admin\", label: \"Global Root Access\", description: \"Direct root execution inside all sandboxes\", allowed: false },\n      { id: \"write:governance\", label: \"Mutate Guardrails\", description: \"Configure global ISO-27001 policy checks\", allowed: false },\n      { id: \"manage:users\", label: \"User Administration\", description: \"Manage operator keys inside own tenant boundaries\", allowed: false },\n      { id: \"manage:clients\", label: \"Tenant Provisioning\", description: \"Spin up and teardown client sandboxes\", allowed: false },\n      { id: \"read:telemetry\", label: \"Global Telemetry\", description: \"Real-time access to tenant-bound telemetry\", allowed: true },\n      { id: \"write:telemetry\", label: \"Modify Telemetry\", description: \"Adjust local enclave parameters\", allowed: false },\n      { id: \"read:projects\", label: \"Global Projects View\", description: \"Inspect local tenant sandbox layers\", allowed: true },\n      { id: \"write:projects\", label: \"Create Sandbox Layers\", description: \"Deploy new isolated project spaces\", allowed: false }\n    ]\n  }\n};\n\nconst INITIAL_OPERATORS: Operator[] = [\n  {\n    id: \"usr-001\",\n    name: \"Alexander Mercer\",\n    email: \"a.mercer@apex-sovereign.gff.ai\",\n    role: \"client_admin\",\n    client: \"Apex Sovereign Group [Preview Client]\",\n    status: \"active\",\n    clearance: \"CLEARANCE LEVEL III (SANDBOX OPERATOR)\",\n    fido2State: \"SECURED (FIDO2)\",\n    lastActive: \"12 mins ago\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"usr-002\",\n    name: \"Dr. Sarah Vance\",\n    email: \"s.vance@governance.gff.ai\",\n    role: \"gff_admin\",\n    client: \"GFF Central Enclave\",\n    status: \"active\",\n    clearance: \"CLEARANCE LEVEL V (SECURE SUPERUSER)\",\n    fido2State: \"SECURED (FIDO2)\",\n    lastActive: \"Active Now\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"usr-003\",\n    name: \"Evelyn Carter\",\n    email: \"e.carter@global-retail.gff.ai\",\n    role: \"client_admin\",\n    client: \"Global Retail Enclave [Preview Client]\",\n    status: \"active\",\n    clearance: \"CLEARANCE LEVEL III (SANDBOX OPERATOR)\",\n    fido2State: \"SECURED (FIDO2)\",\n    lastActive: \"45 mins ago\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"usr-004\",\n    name: \"John Miller\",\n    email: \"j.miller@global-retail.gff.ai\",\n    role: \"client_member\",\n    client: \"Global Retail Enclave [Preview Client]\",\n    status: \"active\",\n    clearance: \"CLEARANCE LEVEL II (TENANT OPERATOR)\",\n    fido2State: \"SECURED (FIDO2)\",\n    lastActive: \"2 hours ago\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"usr-005\",\n    name: \"Marcus Vance\",\n    email: \"m.vance@sovereign-logistics.gff.ai\",\n    role: \"client_admin\",\n    client: \"Sovereign Logistics Unit [Preview Client]\",\n    status: \"pending\",\n    clearance: \"PENDING VERIFICATION\",\n    fido2State: \"NOT REGISTERED\",\n    lastActive: \"Never\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"usr-006\",\n    name: \"Auditor Jenkins\",\n    email: \"j.auditor@compliance.gff.ai\",\n    role: \"client_member\",\n    client: \"Federal Treasury Division [Preview Client]\",\n    status: \"inactive\",\n    clearance: \"CLEARANCE LEVEL IV (TRUST AUDITOR)\",\n    fido2State: \"TOKEN DEACTIVATED\",\n    lastActive: \"3 days ago\"\n  }\n];\n\nexport default function AdminUsersPage() {\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  // 2. STATE VARIABLES\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  const [operators, setOperators] = useState<Operator[]>(INITIAL_OPERATORS);\n  const [selectedOpId, setSelectedOpId] = useState<string>(\"usr-002\");\n  \n  // Filtering & Search state\n  const [searchQuery, setSearchQuery] = useState(\"\");\n  const [roleFilter, setRoleFilter] = useState<\"all\" | \"gff_admin\" | \"client_admin\" | \"client_member\">(\"all\");\n  const [statusFilter, setStatusFilter] = useState<\"all\" | \"active\" | \"pending\" | \"inactive\">(\"all\");\n  \n  // Feedback alerts\n  const [toastMessage, setToastMessage] = useState<{ type: \"success\" | \"info\" | \"warning\"; text: string } | null>(null);\n  \n  // Simulation Modal State\n  const [isInviteModalOpen, setIsInviteModalOpen] = useState(false);\n  const [newOpName, setNewOpName] = useState(\"\");\n  const [newOpEmail, setNewOpEmail] = useState(\"\");\n  const [newOpRole, setNewOpRole] = useState<\"gff_admin\" | \"client_admin\" | \"client_member\">(\"client_member\");\n  const [newOpClient, setNewOpClient] = useState(\"\");\n  const [isHsmHardwareChecked, setIsHsmHardwareChecked] = useState(true);\n\n  // Active / selected operator object lookup\n  const selectedOperator = operators.find(op => op.id === selectedOpId) || operators[0] || INITIAL_OPERATORS[1];\n\n  // Auto-hide toast after 5 seconds\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (toastMessage) {\n      const timer = setTimeout(() => {\n        setToastMessage(null);\n      }, 5000);\n      return () => clearTimeout(timer);\n    }\n  }, [toastMessage]);\n\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  // 3. TOAST TRIGGER UTILITY\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  const triggerToast = (text: string, type: \"success\" | \"info\" | \"warning\" = \"success\") => {\n    setToastMessage({ type, text });\n  };\n\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  // 4. ACTION HANDLERS (LOCAL STATE SIMULATION)\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  \n  // A. Invite User (Adds to state list)\n  const handleInviteUser = (e: React.FormEvent) => {\n    e.preventDefault();\n    if (!newOpName.trim() || !newOpEmail.trim()) {\n      triggerToast(\"Failed to compile invite. Name and secure email are mandatory.\", \"warning\");\n      return;\n    }\n\n    const nextIdNum = Math.max(...operators.map(op => parseInt(op.id.replace(\"usr-\", \"\")))) + 1;\n    const formattedId = `usr-${String(nextIdNum).padStart(3, \"0\")}`;\n    \n    // Auto-calculate clearance based on role\n    let clearanceText = \"CLEARANCE LEVEL II (TENANT OPERATOR)\";\n    if (newOpRole === \"gff_admin\") {\n      clearanceText = \"CLEARANCE LEVEL V (SECURE SUPERUSER)\";\n    } else if (newOpRole === \"client_admin\") {\n      clearanceText = \"CLEARANCE LEVEL III (SANDBOX OPERATOR)\";\n    }\n\n    const targetClient = newOpRole === \"gff_admin\" ? \"GFF Central Enclave\" : (newOpClient || \"Unassigned Sandbox\");\n\n    const newOperator: Operator = {\n      id: formattedId,\n      name: newOpName,\n      email: newOpEmail,\n      role: newOpRole,\n      client: targetClient,\n      status: \"pending\",\n      clearance: clearanceText,\n      fido2State: isHsmHardwareChecked ? \"SECURED (FIDO2)\" : \"NOT REGISTERED\",\n      lastActive: \"Never (Pending Sync)\"\n    };\n\n    setOperators([newOperator, ...operators]);\n    setSelectedOpId(formattedId);\n    setIsInviteModalOpen(false);\n    \n    // Reset Form Fields\n    setNewOpName(\"\");\n    setNewOpEmail(\"\");\n    setNewOpRole(\"client_member\");\n    setNewOpClient(\"\");\n    \n    triggerToast(\n      `SUCCESS: Registered secure SSO invite for ${newOpName}. Activation envelope dispatched to HSM ledger with ID: ${formattedId}.`,\n      \"success\"\n    );\n  };\n\n  // B. Change Role\n  const handleRoleChange = (userId: string, newRole: \"gff_admin\" | \"client_admin\" | \"client_member\") => {\n    let clearanceText = \"CLEARANCE LEVEL II (TENANT OPERATOR)\";\n    if (newRole === \"gff_admin\") {\n      clearanceText = \"CLEARANCE LEVEL V (SECURE SUPERUSER)\";\n    } else if (newRole === \"client_admin\") {\n      clearanceText = \"CLEARANCE LEVEL III (SANDBOX OPERATOR)\";\n    }\n\n    setOperators(prev => prev.map(op => {\n      if (op.id === userId) {\n        return {\n          ...op,\n          role: newRole,\n          clearance: clearanceText,\n          // If moving to gff_admin, default client association to GFF Central Enclave\n          client: newRole === \"gff_admin\" ? \"GFF Central Enclave\" : (op.client === \"GFF Central Enclave\" ? \"Apex Sovereign Group [Preview Client]\" : op.client)\n        };\n      }\n      return op;\n    }));\n\n    const targetName = operators.find(op => op.id === userId)?.name || \"Operator\";\n    triggerToast(`DIRECTORY SYNCED: Elevation state updated. ${targetName} granted ${ROLE_DETAILS[newRole].label}.`, \"success\");\n  };\n\n  // C. Toggle Activation/Deactivation\n  const handleToggleActivation = (userId: string) => {\n    let updatedStatus: \"active\" | \"inactive\" = \"active\";\n    let updatedFido: \"SECURED (FIDO2)\" | \"TOKEN DEACTIVATED\" = \"SECURED (FIDO2)\";\n    const op = operators.find(o => o.id === userId);\n    \n    if (!op) return;\n\n    if (op.status === \"active\") {\n      updatedStatus = \"inactive\";\n      updatedFido = \"TOKEN DEACTIVATED\";\n    } else {\n      updatedStatus = \"active\";\n      updatedFido = \"SECURED (FIDO2)\";\n    }\n\n    setOperators(prev => prev.map(o => {\n      if (o.id === userId) {\n        return {\n          ...o,\n          status: updatedStatus,\n          fido2State: updatedFido,\n          lastActive: updatedStatus === \"inactive\" ? \"Revoked\" : \"Active Now\"\n        };\n      }\n      return o;\n    }));\n\n    if (updatedStatus === \"inactive\") {\n      triggerToast(`SECURITY EVENT: Terminated session keys for ${op.name}. Client gateway tokens invalidated.`, \"warning\");\n    } else {\n      triggerToast(`SECURITY EVENT: Restored authentication pathway for ${op.name}. SSO session state ACTIVE.`, \"success\");\n    }\n  };\n\n  // D. Reset Hardware Token / Access Preview\n  const handleResetAccess = (userId: string) => {\n    setOperators(prev => prev.map(o => {\n      if (o.id === userId) {\n        return {\n          ...o,\n          fido2State: \"ROLLED-OVER\",\n          lastActive: \"Active Now\"\n        };\n      }\n      return o;\n    }));\n\n    const target = operators.find(o => o.id === userId);\n    triggerToast(\n      `HSM ROLLOVER: Hardware token revoked for ${target?.name || \"operator\"}. Dispatched physical OTP key material envelope. SHA-256 fingerprint signed: GFF_SIG_0x7BB20A...`,\n      \"info\"\n    );\n  };\n\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  // 5. FILTER WORKFLOW\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  const filteredOperators = operators.filter(op => {\n    // Search query matches name, email, client domain, or id\n    const matchesSearch = \n      op.name.toLowerCase().includes(searchQuery.toLowerCase()) ||\n      op.email.toLowerCase().includes(searchQuery.toLowerCase()) ||\n      op.client.toLowerCase().includes(searchQuery.toLowerCase()) ||\n      op.id.toLowerCase().includes(searchQuery.toLowerCase());\n\n    const matchesRole = roleFilter === \"all\" || op.role === roleFilter;\n    const matchesStatus = statusFilter === \"all\" || op.status === statusFilter;\n\n    return matchesSearch && matchesRole && matchesStatus;\n  });\n\n  // Calculate live statistics for metrics cards\n  const totalOpsCount = operators.length;\n  const activeOpsCount = operators.filter(op => op.status === \"active\").length;\n  const pendingOpsCount = operators.filter(op => op.status === \"pending\").length;\n  const gffAdminCount = operators.filter(op => op.role === \"gff_admin\").length;\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"space-y-6 text-white pb-12 font-sans relative\">\n      \n      {/* Subtle background architecture visual grid pattern */}\n      <div className=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.03] select-none bg-[radial-gradient(#00FFC2_1.5px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:24px_24px] rounded-xl -z-10\" />\n\n      {/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n          A. NOTIFICATION BANNER (PHASE 4 AUTH / DB DISCLAIMER)\n          --------------------------------------------------------------------------- */}\n      <div className=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500/10 via-amber-600/5 to-transparent border border-amber-500/20 rounded-xl p-4 flex gap-3.5 items-start\">\n        <div className=\"p-2 bg-amber-500/10 rounded-lg text-amber-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0 border border-amber-500/10\">\n          <ShieldAlert className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n        </div>\n        <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n          <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-amber-400 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono\">\n            Cryptographic Sandbox Simulation (Phase 4 Oversight)\n          </h4>\n          <p className=\"text-xs text-white/70 leading-relaxed max-w-5xl\">\n            This administration panel demonstrates frontend role management and local-only Role-Based Access Control (RBAC). \n            Actions are safely sandboxed in-memory. Database syncing, real OAuth2/SAML SSO integrations, and HSM key distribution \n            are scoped for the Phase 5 infrastructure deploy.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n          B. TITLE HEADER & PRIMARY ACTIONS\n          --------------------------------------------------------------------------- */}\n      <div className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4 pt-1\">\n        <div>\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n            <span className=\"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FFC2] animate-pulse\" />\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] text-[#00FFC2] font-mono tracking-widest uppercase font-bold\">\n              Secure Oversight Command\n            </span>\n          </div>\n          <h1 className=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white font-mono uppercase mt-0.5\">\n            System Operators & RBAC\n          </h1>\n          <p className=\"text-xs text-white/50 mt-1\">\n            Audit root clearance keys, register tenant admins, map hardware SSO tokens, and update authorization scopes across active enclaves.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <button\n          onClick={() => setIsInviteModalOpen(true)}\n          className=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-[#00FFC2]/10 hover:bg-[#00FFC2]/20 text-[#00FFC2] border border-[#00FFC2]/30 hover:border-[#00FFC2]/50 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-bold transition-all duration-200 self-start md:self-auto hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,255,194,0.15)] group\"\n        >\n          <Plus className=\"w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:rotate-90\" />\n          INVITE SYSTEM OPERATOR\n        </button>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n          C. FEEDBACK TOAST/ALERT\n          --------------------------------------------------------------------------- */}\n      {toastMessage && (\n        <div className={`border rounded-xl p-3.5 flex items-start gap-3 transition-all duration-300 animate-fadeIn ${\n          toastMessage.type === \"success\" \n            ? \"bg-emerald-500/10 border-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-300\"\n            : toastMessage.type === \"warning\"\n            ? \"bg-rose-500/10 border-rose-500/20 text-rose-300\"\n            : \"bg-[#009DFF]/10 border-[#009DFF]/20 text-blue-300\"\n        }`}>\n          {toastMessage.type === \"success\" && <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-5 h-5 shrink-0 text-emerald-400 mt-0.5\" />}\n          {toastMessage.type === \"warning\" && <AlertTriangle className=\"w-5 h-5 shrink-0 text-rose-400 mt-0.5\" />}\n          {toastMessage.type === \"info\" && <Info className=\"w-5 h-5 shrink-0 text-blue-400 mt-0.5\" />}\n          <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-wider block\">\n              System Notification Log\n            </span>\n            <p className=\"text-xs leading-relaxed text-white/90\">{toastMessage.text}</p>\n          </div>\n          <button \n            onClick={() => setToastMessage(null)}\n            className=\"ml-auto text-white/40 hover:text-white/80 transition-colors shrink-0\"\n          >\n            <X className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n          </button>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n          D. PREMIUM KPI METRICS CARDS (NARRATIVE GRAPHIC STATE)\n          --------------------------------------------------------------------------- */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\n        {/* Card 1: Total Users */}\n        <div className=\"bg-[#08080c]/60 border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-4 space-y-3 hover:border-white/10 transition-all duration-300 group\">\n          <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider\">\n              System Accounts\n            </span>\n            <div className=\"p-1.5 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/60\">\n              <User className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <h3 className=\"text-2xl font-bold font-mono text-white tracking-tight\">\n              {totalOpsCount} <span className=\"text-xs text-white/30 font-normal\">Registered</span>\n            </h3>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[10px] text-white/50\">\n              <span className=\"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FFC2]\" />\n              <span>{activeOpsCount} Active directories validated</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Card 2: Global Admins */}\n        <div className=\"bg-[#08080c]/60 border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-4 space-y-3 hover:border-white/10 transition-all duration-300 group\">\n          <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider\">\n              Global Root Clearances\n            </span>\n            <div className=\"p-1.5 rounded-lg bg-red-500/5 border border-red-500/10 text-red-400\">\n              <Shield className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <h3 className=\"text-2xl font-bold font-mono text-red-400 tracking-tight\">\n              {gffAdminCount} <span className=\"text-xs text-white/30 font-normal\">Superusers</span>\n            </h3>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[10px] text-white/50\">\n              <span className=\"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/80\" />\n              <span>FIDO2 multi-factor enforced</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Card 3: Client Admins / Members */}\n        <div className=\"bg-[#08080c]/60 border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-4 space-y-3 hover:border-white/10 transition-all duration-300 group\">\n          <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider\">\n              Tenant Sandboxes\n            </span>\n            <div className=\"p-1.5 rounded-lg bg-[#009DFF]/5 border border-[#009DFF]/10 text-[#009DFF]\">\n              <Building className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <h3 className=\"text-2xl font-bold font-mono text-white tracking-tight\">\n              {operators.filter(o => o.role !== \"gff_admin\").length} <span className=\"text-xs text-white/30 font-normal\">Operators</span>\n            </h3>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[10px] text-white/50\">\n              <span className=\"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF]\" />\n              <span>Sovereign client tenant bounds</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Card 4: SSO State */}\n        <div className=\"bg-[#08080c]/60 border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-4 space-y-3 hover:border-white/10 transition-all duration-300 group\">\n          <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider\">\n              Enclave Registrations\n            </span>\n            <div className=\"p-1.5 rounded-lg bg-amber-500/5 border border-amber-500/10 text-amber-400\">\n              <Fingerprint className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <h3 className=\"text-2xl font-bold font-mono text-amber-400 tracking-tight\">\n              {pendingOpsCount} <span className=\"text-xs text-white/30 font-normal\">Pending Keys</span>\n            </h3>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[10px] text-white/50\">\n              <span className=\"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-500 animate-pulse\" />\n              <span>Awaiting secure handshake</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n          E. INTERACTIVE FILTERS BAR\n          --------------------------------------------------------------------------- */}\n      <div className=\"bg-[#040406]/90 border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-4 flex flex-col gap-4\">\n        <div className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4\">\n          \n          {/* Left: Search input */}\n          <div className=\"relative flex-1 max-w-md\">\n            <Search className=\"absolute left-3 top-2.5 h-4 w-4 text-white/30\" />\n            <input\n              type=\"text\"\n              placeholder=\"Search operators by name, email, or linked tenant...\"\n              value={searchQuery}\n              onChange={(e) => setSearchQuery(e.target.value)}\n              className=\"w-full bg-[#08080c]/60 border border-white/10 rounded-lg pl-9 pr-4 py-2 text-xs text-white placeholder-white/30 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#00FFC2] focus:border-transparent font-mono transition-all\"\n            />\n            {searchQuery && (\n              <button\n                onClick={() => setSearchQuery(\"\")}\n                className=\"absolute right-3 top-2 text-white/40 hover:text-white\"\n              >\n                <X className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n              </button>\n            )}\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Right: Role & Status Pill Toggles */}\n          <div className=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 text-xs font-mono\">\n            {/* Role filter */}\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n              <span className=\"text-white/40 uppercase font-bold text-[10px]\">Role:</span>\n              <div className=\"flex bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-0.5 overflow-hidden\">\n                {([\"all\", \"gff_admin\", \"client_admin\", \"client_member\"] as const).map((r) => (\n                  <button\n                    key={r}\n                    onClick={() => setRoleFilter(r)}\n                    className={`px-2.5 py-1 rounded text-[10px] uppercase font-bold transition-all ${\n                      roleFilter === r\n                        ? \"bg-white/10 text-[#00FFC2] shadow-sm\"\n                        : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white/70\"\n                    }`}\n                  >\n                    {r === \"all\" ? \"All\" : r.replace(\"_\", \" \")}\n                  </button>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Status filter */}\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n              <span className=\"text-white/40 uppercase font-bold text-[10px]\">Status:</span>\n              <div className=\"flex bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-0.5 overflow-hidden\">\n                {([\"all\", \"active\", \"pending\", \"inactive\"] as const).map((s) => (\n                  <button\n                    key={s}\n                    onClick={() => setStatusFilter(s)}\n                    className={`px-2.5 py-1 rounded text-[10px] uppercase font-bold transition-all ${\n                      statusFilter === s\n                        ? \"bg-white/10 text-white font-bold\"\n                        : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white/70\"\n                    }`}\n                  >\n                    {s}\n                  </button>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n          F. MAIN SPLIT SECTION (BENTO GRID STYLE)\n          --------------------------------------------------------------------------- */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-12 gap-6 items-start\">\n        \n        {/* LEFT COMPONENT: HIGH-FIDELITY INTERACTIVE DIRECTORY TABLE (7 cols) */}\n        <div className=\"xl:col-span-8 bg-[#040406]/80 border border-white/5 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl backdrop-blur-sm\">\n          \n          <div className=\"px-5 py-4 border-b border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] flex items-center justify-between\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n              <Server className=\"w-4 h-4 text-white/40\" />\n              <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                Operator Directory Ledger ({filteredOperators.length} found)\n              </h3>\n            </div>\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/30 font-mono\">\n              SECURE INDEX_SSO_v2.6\n            </span>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n            <table className=\"w-full text-left border-collapse font-mono\">\n              <thead>\n                <tr className=\"border-b border-white/5 text-[9.5px] uppercase text-white/40 tracking-wider bg-white/[0.01]\">\n                  <th className=\"py-3 px-4 font-bold\">Secure Identity / Profile</th>\n                  <th className=\"py-3 px-4 font-bold\">Enclave Association</th>\n                  <th className=\"py-3 px-4 font-bold\">Security Role</th>\n                  <th className=\"py-3 px-4 font-bold\">Session State</th>\n                  <th className=\"py-3 px-4 font-bold text-right\">SSO Credential</th>\n                </tr>\n              </thead>\n              <tbody className=\"divide-y divide-white/[0.03] text-xs\">\n                {filteredOperators.length === 0 ? (\n                  <tr>\n                    <td colSpan={5} className=\"py-12 text-center text-white/30\">\n                      <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                        <UserX className=\"w-8 h-8 mx-auto opacity-20 text-white\" />\n                        <p className=\"text-xs font-bold\">NO ALIGNED OPERATORS FOUND</p>\n                        <p className=\"text-[10.5px] text-white/40 max-w-md mx-auto\">\n                          No registration entries match the active filter criteria. Clear your search querying or reset the filters.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </td>\n                  </tr>\n                ) : (\n                  filteredOperators.map((op) => {\n                    const isSelected = op.id === selectedOpId;\n                    const details = ROLE_DETAILS[op.role];\n                    \n                    // Simple initials generator\n                    const initials = op.name\n                      .split(\" \")\n                      .map(n => n[0])\n                      .join(\"\")\n                      .toUpperCase()\n                      .substring(0, 2);\n\n                    return (\n                      <tr \n                        key={op.id}\n                        onClick={() => setSelectedOpId(op.id)}\n                        className={`cursor-pointer transition-all duration-150 group border-l-2 ${\n                          isSelected \n                            ? \"bg-white/[0.03] border-l-[#00FFC2]\" \n                            : \"border-l-transparent hover:bg-white/[0.01] hover:border-l-white/20\"\n                        }`}\n                      >\n                        {/* Name & Identity info */}\n                        <td className=\"py-3.5 px-4\">\n                          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n                            <div className={`w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-[11px] border shrink-0 transition-all ${\n                              isSelected \n                                ? \"bg-[#00FFC2]/10 text-[#00FFC2] border-[#00FFC2]/30\" \n                                : \"bg-white/5 text-white/70 border-white/10 group-hover:border-white/20\"\n                            }`}>\n                              {initials}\n                            </div>\n                            <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                              <span className={`block font-bold text-xs transition-colors ${\n                                isSelected ? \"text-[#00FFC2]\" : \"text-white group-hover:text-white\"\n                              }`}>\n                                {op.name}\n                              </span>\n                              <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 block leading-none\">\n                                {op.email}\n                              </span>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                        </td>\n\n                        {/* Linked client */}\n                        <td className=\"py-3.5 px-4 text-white/70 text-[11px]\">\n                          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                            <Building className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white/30\" />\n                            <span className=\"truncate max-w-[150px] font-medium\" title={op.client}>\n                              {op.client}\n                            </span>\n                          </div>\n                        </td>\n\n                        {/* Assigned role badge */}\n                        <td className=\"py-3.5 px-4\">\n                          <span className={`inline-flex items-center rounded border px-2 py-0.5 text-[9px] font-bold uppercase ${details.badgeColor}`}>\n                            {op.role.replace(\"_\", \" \")}\n                          </span>\n                        </td>\n\n                        {/* Active session status */}\n                        <td className=\"py-3.5 px-4\">\n                          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                            <span className={`h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full ${\n                              op.status === \"active\" \n                                ? \"bg-emerald-400 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(52,211,153,0.5)] animate-pulse\" \n                                : op.status === \"pending\"\n                                ? \"bg-amber-400 animate-pulse\"\n                                : \"bg-zinc-500\"\n                            }`} />\n                            <span className={`text-[10px] uppercase font-bold ${\n                              op.status === \"active\" \n                                ? \"text-emerald-400\" \n                                : op.status === \"pending\"\n                                ? \"text-amber-400\"\n                                : \"text-zinc-500\"\n                            }`}>\n                              {op.status}\n                            </span>\n                          </div>\n                        </td>\n\n                        {/* Credentials State */}\n                        <td className=\"py-3.5 px-4 text-right\">\n                          <div className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 justify-end\">\n                            {op.fido2State === \"SECURED (FIDO2)\" && (\n                              <>\n                                <Lock className=\"w-3 h-3 text-emerald-400\" />\n                                <span className=\"text-[10px] text-emerald-400 font-bold\">FIDO2 SECURE</span>\n                              </>\n                            )}\n                            {op.fido2State === \"ROLLED-OVER\" && (\n                              <>\n                                <RefreshCw className=\"w-3 h-3 text-blue-400 animate-spin\" />\n                                <span className=\"text-[10px] text-blue-400 font-bold\">KEY ROLLING</span>\n                              </>\n                            )}\n                            {op.fido2State === \"NOT REGISTERED\" && (\n                              <>\n                                <HelpCircle className=\"w-3 h-3 text-amber-400\" />\n                                <span className=\"text-[10px] text-amber-400\">UNREGISTERED</span>\n                              </>\n                            )}\n                            {op.fido2State === \"TOKEN DEACTIVATED\" && (\n                              <>\n                                <Unlock className=\"w-3 h-3 text-zinc-500\" />\n                                <span className=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500\">DEACTIVATED</span>\n                              </>\n                            )}\n                          </div>\n                          <span className=\"block text-[9px] text-white/30 mt-0.5 leading-none\">\n                            ID: {op.id.toUpperCase()}\n                          </span>\n                        </td>\n                      </tr>\n                    );\n                  })\n                )}\n              </tbody>\n            </table>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"p-4 border-t border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40\">\n            <div>\n              Displaying <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{filteredOperators.length}</span> of <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{operators.length}</span> total administrative operator entities.\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"flex gap-2\">\n              <span className=\"px-2 py-0.5 bg-white/5 rounded border border-white/10 text-white/60\">\n                ACTIVE SSO ENVIRONMENT\n              </span>\n              <span className=\"px-2 py-0.5 bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 rounded border border-emerald-500/20\">\n                HEALTHY\n              </span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n\n        {/* RIGHT COMPONENT: DETAILED ACCESS CONTROL & SIMULATED AUDIT PANEL (4 cols) */}\n        <div className=\"xl:col-span-4 space-y-6\">\n          \n          <div className=\"bg-[#040406]/90 border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-5 space-y-5 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden\">\n            {/* Visual background indicator box accent */}\n            <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top_right,rgba(0,255,194,0.04),transparent_50%)] pointer-events-none\" />\n\n            <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-4 space-y-1\">\n              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#00FFC2] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                <Fingerprint className=\"w-3 h-3\" /> SECURITY PROFILE DETAILS\n              </span>\n              <h3 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider truncate\">\n                {selectedOperator.name}\n              </h3>\n              <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/40 truncate font-mono\">\n                {selectedOperator.email}\n              </p>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Quick Stats Grid */}\n            <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 font-mono text-[11px]\">\n              <div className=\"bg-[#020202]/50 border border-white/5 rounded-lg p-2.5 space-y-1\">\n                <span className=\"text-white/30 text-[9px] block uppercase font-bold leading-none\">Security ID</span>\n                <span className=\"text-white font-bold text-xs\">{selectedOperator.id.toUpperCase()}</span>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"bg-[#020202]/50 border border-white/5 rounded-lg p-2.5 space-y-1\">\n                <span className=\"text-white/30 text-[9px] block uppercase font-bold leading-none\">SSO Telemetry</span>\n                <span className=\"text-amber-400 font-bold text-xs truncate block\" title={selectedOperator.clearance}>\n                  {selectedOperator.clearance.replace(\"CLEARANCE \", \"\")}\n                </span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Live simulator actions section */}\n            <div className=\"space-y-3.5 pt-2\">\n              <h4 className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider\">\n                Access Level & Credentials Control\n              </h4>\n\n              {/* ACTION A: Modify Role Select */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/50 block font-bold\">\n                  Assigned Clearance Role:\n                </label>\n                <div className=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-0.5\">\n                  {([\"gff_admin\", \"client_admin\", \"client_member\"] as const).map((r) => {\n                    const isCurrent = selectedOperator.role === r;\n                    return (\n                      <button\n                        key={r}\n                        onClick={() => handleRoleChange(selectedOperator.id, r)}\n                        className={`py-1.5 rounded text-[9.5px] font-mono uppercase font-bold transition-all ${\n                          isCurrent\n                            ? \"bg-white/10 text-[#00FFC2] font-extrabold shadow-sm\"\n                            : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white/60\"\n                        }`}\n                      >\n                        {r.split(\"_\")[1]}\n                      </button>\n                    );\n                  })}\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Action trigger buttons */}\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 font-mono\">\n                {/* ACTION B: Toggle Activation status */}\n                <button\n                  onClick={() => handleToggleActivation(selectedOperator.id)}\n                  className={`flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-2 border rounded-lg text-[10px] font-bold transition-all ${\n                    selectedOperator.status === \"active\"\n                      ? \"bg-rose-500/10 hover:bg-rose-500/20 text-rose-400 border-rose-500/20 hover:border-rose-500/35\"\n                      : \"bg-emerald-500/10 hover:bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 border-emerald-500/20 hover:border-emerald-500/35\"\n                  }`}\n                >\n                  {selectedOperator.status === \"active\" ? (\n                    <>\n                      <UserX className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 shrink-0\" />\n                      DEACTIVATE OP\n                    </>\n                  ) : (\n                    <>\n                      <UserCheck className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 shrink-0\" />\n                      ACTIVATE OP\n                    </>\n                  )}\n                </button>\n\n                {/* ACTION C: Reset hardware credentials */}\n                <button\n                  onClick={() => handleResetAccess(selectedOperator.id)}\n                  className=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-2 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 text-white/80 hover:text-white rounded-lg text-[10px] font-bold transition-all\"\n                >\n                  <Key className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 shrink-0\" />\n                  RESET FIDO2 KEY\n                </button>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* REAL-TIME DYNAMIC PERMISSIONS LIST */}\n            <div className=\"space-y-3 pt-3 border-t border-white/5\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider\">\n                  Cryptographic Clearance Scopes\n                </span>\n                <span className=\"text-[9px] bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-white/50 font-mono uppercase\">\n                  {selectedOperator.role.replace(\"_\", \" \")}\n                </span>\n              </div>\n              \n              <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 leading-relaxed font-mono\">\n                {ROLE_DETAILS[selectedOperator.role].description}\n              </p>\n\n              <div className=\"space-y-1.5 max-h-[220px] overflow-y-auto pr-1\">\n                {ROLE_DETAILS[selectedOperator.role].scopes.map((scope) => (\n                  <div \n                    key={scope.id}\n                    className=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3 p-2 rounded bg-[#020202]/40 border border-white/5 text-[10.5px] font-mono\"\n                  >\n                    <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white font-bold block\">{scope.label}</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 block leading-tight\">{scope.description}</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"shrink-0 pt-0.5\">\n                      {scope.allowed ? (\n                        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-emerald-400 font-bold bg-emerald-500/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[8.5px] border border-emerald-500/20\">\n                          <Check className=\"w-3 h-3\" /> ALLOWED\n                        </div>\n                      ) : (\n                        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-zinc-500 font-bold bg-zinc-500/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[8.5px] border border-zinc-500/10\">\n                          <Lock className=\"w-3 h-3\" /> DENIED\n                        </div>\n                      )}\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Secure Node audit timeline widget */}\n          <div className=\"bg-[#040406]/90 border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-5 space-y-4\">\n            <h4 className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n              <Clock className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" /> SSO SYSTEM AUDIT TRAIL\n            </h4>\n            \n            <div className=\"space-y-3 text-[11px] font-mono\">\n              <div className=\"relative pl-4 border-l border-white/10 space-y-1\">\n                <span className=\"absolute -left-[4.5px] top-1.5 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400\" />\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 block leading-none\">TODAY, 12:22:18</span>\n                <p className=\"text-white/80 font-bold leading-snug\">Handshake session validated</p>\n                <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40\">Dr. Sarah Vance signed credential ledger under epoch_4.</p>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"relative pl-4 border-l border-white/10 space-y-1\">\n                <span className=\"absolute -left-[4.5px] top-1.5 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-amber-400\" />\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 block leading-none\">TODAY, 10:45:00</span>\n                <p className=\"text-white/80 font-bold leading-snug\">Registration invite sent</p>\n                <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40\">Dispatched registration envelope for Marcus Vance.</p>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"relative pl-4 border-l border-white/10 space-y-1\">\n                <span className=\"absolute -left-[4.5px] top-1.5 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-zinc-500\" />\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 block leading-none\">YESTERDAY, 09:12:11</span>\n                <p className=\"text-white/60 font-medium leading-snug\">FIDO2 token revoked</p>\n                <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40\">Auditor Jenkins revoked on Federal Treasury enclave.</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n          G. MODAL: INVITE SYSTEM OPERATOR (SIMULATED REGISTER FORM)\n          --------------------------------------------------------------------------- */}\n      {isInviteModalOpen && (\n        <div className=\"fixed inset-0 bg-black/85 backdrop-blur-md flex items-center justify-center p-4 z-50 animate-fadeIn\">\n          <div className=\"bg-[#0a0a0e] border border-white/10 rounded-2xl w-full max-w-lg overflow-hidden shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)] font-mono\">\n            \n            {/* Modal Header */}\n            <div className=\"px-6 py-4 border-b border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between bg-white/[0.01]\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                <UserCheck className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#00FFC2]\" />\n                <h3 className=\"text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white\">\n                  Invite System Operator\n                </h3>\n              </div>\n              <button \n                onClick={() => setIsInviteModalOpen(false)}\n                className=\"text-white/40 hover:text-white transition-colors\"\n              >\n                <X className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n              </button>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Modal Form */}\n            <form onSubmit={handleInviteUser} className=\"p-6 space-y-4\">\n              \n              <div className=\"bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/20 rounded-lg p-3 text-[10.5px] text-amber-400 leading-normal\">\n                🔑 NOTICE: Invites instantly populate this local system registry preview. Physical keys and SSO email routes will simulate success without issuing external mail.\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Full Name */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <label className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 block font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                  Operator Full Name:\n                </label>\n                <div className=\"relative\">\n                  <User className=\"absolute left-3 top-2.5 h-4 w-4 text-white/30\" />\n                  <input\n                    type=\"text\"\n                    required\n                    placeholder=\"e.g. Jane Doe\"\n                    value={newOpName}\n                    onChange={(e) => setNewOpName(e.target.value)}\n                    className=\"w-full bg-[#020202]/60 border border-white/10 rounded-lg pl-9 pr-4 py-2 text-xs text-white placeholder-white/30 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#00FFC2]\"\n                  />\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Secure Email */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <label className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 block font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                  Secure Enterprise Email:\n                </label>\n                <div className=\"relative\">\n                  <Mail className=\"absolute left-3 top-2.5 h-4 w-4 text-white/30\" />\n                  <input\n                    type=\"email\"\n                    required\n                    placeholder=\"e.g. j.doe@apex-sovereign.gff.ai\"\n                    value={newOpEmail}\n                    onChange={(e) => setNewOpEmail(e.target.value)}\n                    className=\"w-full bg-[#020202]/60 border border-white/10 rounded-lg pl-9 pr-4 py-2 text-xs text-white placeholder-white/30 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#00FFC2]\"\n                  />\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Role Radio Grid */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                <label className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 block font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                  Target Access Role (RBAC):\n                </label>\n                <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2\">\n                  <label className={`border rounded-lg p-2.5 flex flex-col justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all ${\n                    newOpRole === \"client_member\"\n                      ? \"bg-white/5 border-[#00FFC2]/50 text-[#00FFC2]\"\n                      : \"bg-[#020202]/40 border-white/5 text-white/50 hover:border-white/10\"\n                  }`}>\n                    <input\n                      type=\"radio\"\n                      name=\"opRole\"\n                      value=\"client_member\"\n                      checked={newOpRole === \"client_member\"}\n                      onChange={() => setNewOpRole(\"client_member\")}\n                      className=\"sr-only\"\n                    />\n                    <span className=\"text-[11px] font-bold block\">Member</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-[8.5px] leading-tight block mt-1 text-white/30\">\n                      Standard sandbox operator credentials\n                    </span>\n                  </label>\n\n                  <label className={`border rounded-lg p-2.5 flex flex-col justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all ${\n                    newOpRole === \"client_admin\"\n                      ? \"bg-white/5 border-[#009DFF]/50 text-[#009DFF]\"\n                      : \"bg-[#020202]/40 border-white/5 text-white/50 hover:border-white/10\"\n                  }`}>\n                    <input\n                      type=\"radio\"\n                      name=\"opRole\"\n                      value=\"client_admin\"\n                      checked={newOpRole === \"client_admin\"}\n                      onChange={() => setNewOpRole(\"client_admin\")}\n                      className=\"sr-only\"\n                    />\n                    <span className=\"text-[11px] font-bold block text-inherit\">Tenant Admin</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-[8.5px] leading-tight block mt-1 text-white/30\">\n                      Enclave scope administrator keys\n                    </span>\n                  </label>\n\n                  <label className={`border rounded-lg p-2.5 flex flex-col justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all ${\n                    newOpRole === \"gff_admin\"\n                      ? \"bg-white/5 border-red-500/50 text-red-400\"\n                      : \"bg-[#020202]/40 border-white/5 text-white/50 hover:border-white/10\"\n                  }`}>\n                    <input\n                      type=\"radio\"\n                      name=\"opRole\"\n                      value=\"gff_admin\"\n                      checked={newOpRole === \"gff_admin\"}\n                      onChange={() => setNewOpRole(\"gff_admin\")}\n                      className=\"sr-only\"\n                    />\n                    <span className=\"text-[11px] font-bold block text-inherit\">Global Admin</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-[8.5px] leading-tight block mt-1 text-white/30\">\n                      Global superuser credentials\n                    </span>\n                  </label>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Client Account Association selector */}\n              {newOpRole !== \"gff_admin\" && (\n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <label className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 block font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                    Link Enclave Client Account:\n                  </label>\n                  <select\n                    value={newOpClient}\n                    onChange={(e) => setNewOpClient(e.target.value)}\n                    className=\"w-full bg-[#020202]/60 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-xs text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#00FFC2]\"\n                  >\n                    <option value=\"\">-- Choose Sandbox Tenant Account --</option>\n                    {previewClientAccounts.map((client) => (\n                      <option key={client.id} value={client.name}>\n                        {client.name}\n                      </option>\n                    ))}\n                  </select>\n                </div>\n              )}\n\n              {/* Toggle Hardware Token checkbox */}\n              <div className=\"pt-2\">\n                <label className=\"flex items-center gap-2.5 cursor-pointer text-[10px] text-white/60\">\n                  <input\n                    type=\"checkbox\"\n                    checked={isHsmHardwareChecked}\n                    onChange={(e) => setIsHsmHardwareChecked(e.target.checked)}\n                    className=\"rounded bg-black border-white/10 text-[#00FFC2] focus:ring-0\"\n                  />\n                  <span>Enforce instant HSM hardware keypair registration (FIDO2)</span>\n                </label>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Form Buttons */}\n              <div className=\"flex items-center justify-end gap-3 pt-4 border-t border-white/5\">\n                <button\n                  type=\"button\"\n                  onClick={() => setIsInviteModalOpen(false)}\n                  className=\"px-4 py-2 text-xs text-white/40 hover:text-white transition-colors\"\n                >\n                  CANCEL\n                </button>\n                <button\n                  type=\"submit\"\n                  className=\"bg-[#00FFC2]/10 hover:bg-[#00FFC2]/20 border border-[#00FFC2]/30 hover:border-[#00FFC2]/50 text-[#00FFC2] px-5 py-2 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold transition-all\"\n                >\n                  DISPATCH INVITE\n                </button>\n              </div>\n\n            </form>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
