e client selection dropdown to ensure it's intuitive and visually appealing. I'm also ensuring the dropdown only shows up for non-admin users.\n\n\n**Refining Submission Button**\n\nI'm now refining the visual presentation and functionality of the \"DISPATCH INVITE\" submission button. I'm focusing on its visual style, making the color and font more appealing. I'm also ensuring the functionality is fully integrated within the form submission process and responding to different actions.\n\n\n"}}
